### Get all carts
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/carts/
Content-Type: application/json

### Create cart
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/carts/
Content-Type: application/json


### Get specific cart
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/carts/{cart_id}/
Content-Type: application/json

### Update cart (PUT)
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/carts/{cart_id}/
Content-Type: application/json

### Delete cart
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/carts/{cart_id}/
Content-Type: application/json

### Get all cart items
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/cart-items/
Content-Type: application/json
{

}

### Create cart item
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/cart-items/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "product_id": "{product_id}",
    "quantity": 2
}

### Get specific cart item
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/cart-items/{item_id}/
Content-Type: application/json

### Update cart item (PUT)
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/cart-items/{item_id}/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "product_id": "{product_id}",
    "quantity": 5
}

### Update cart item (PATCH)
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/cart-items/{item_id}/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "quantity": 3
}

### Delete cart item
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/cart/cart-items/{item_id}/
Content-Type: application/json
